parameters: \SE[8]I wonder if Laura and the others are okay...?

\SE[20]Hey, Luna...? We might die like this... \!\SE[19]Can I ask
you for a little favor?

\SE[29]I've been so busy all this time... \SE[25]I couldn't bring
myself to say it though.

\SE[21]I wanted to travel to various places together... \SE[19]I
wanted to create many memories together... \SE[19]I wanted to see
various sceneries together...

\SE[30]Hehe... That sounds fun... \!\SE[31]Travel, huh... Where
does Laura want to go?

\SE[21]Ah... That's right. I want to... see the ocean....
\SE[19]I've never been there before.

\SE[16]The ocean, huh... \SE[15]I only know about it from
books... It must be really fun...

\SE[92] (For some reason, it has become a completely two-person
world...)

\SE[44] (Maybe it has become a hopeless situation... \!\SE[45] I
guess they were unfortunately saved...)

\SE[68]Both of you... It would be better to keep unnecessary
flirting to a minimum...

\SE[22]Huh...? \.I think I heard a voice that sounded like
Vita...?
\SE[32]I wonder...? \!\SE[30]I can only hear your voice...

\SE[31]I want to exchange words with you as much as possible.
\!\SE[30]Let's talk more, shall we...?

\SE[42]Hey... Laura. \SE[43]Um, I know it's not the best time,
but...

\SE[42]When I was watching Laura... I started feeling strange...
\SE[44]Um... Is it okay to do naughty things...?

\SE[29]A-At a time like this...? \!\SE[25]Well... I guess there's
no helping it...

\SE[94]Stop! Stop it!! You guys!! \SE[91]Cut it out! Especially
you, Lunaroa! \SE[92]Vita is watching too!

\SE[14]What... Vega...!! \SE[13]You have no right to stop me...!!
\SE[12]......\.......\.......\.\SE[4]Huh?
\SE[59]... It's too specific for a hallucination...

\SE[16]Um... What is this...? \!\SE[60]What kind of situation is
this...?

It seems to be called a 'life support system.' It appears to
provide the body with necessary nutrients and oxygen. However,
I'm not quite sure about the exact mechanism.
